Ralph R. STRANGE v. COMMISSIONER OF INTERNAL REVENUE. No. 7278. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Sept. 6, 1933.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Cirenit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of respondent, consented to by petitioner, ordered petition to review in this cause dismissed; mandate forthwith.
